column4: "W. A. Mozart - (Formerly called) Symphony No. 37 in G Major
"Introduction to a symphony in G Major by Michael Haydn - Adagio maestoso"
"Symphony No. 37 was previously credited to Mozart. It has later been determined  "
"only the introduction is by him. The remainder is by Michael Haydn"
"W. A. Mozart - Introduction to a Symphony in G Major by Michael Haydn (Ex. K.444)"
